        {
            "title": "聯想楊元慶：DeepSeek為AI平民化提供更現實路徑 符合集團混合式AI願景",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯想(00992)董事長兼首席執行官楊元慶在集團派季度業績之際，亦向員工發內部信，當中提到近期熱爆的DeepSeek。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：聯想官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241118_FI_source-web_00992.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：聯想官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241118_FI_source-web_00992.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：聯想官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地媒體引述上述內部信的內容，指出楊元慶認為DeepSeek模型以其更高的推理效率和更低的算力成本，為AI平民化和應用落地提供了更加現實的路徑，有助加速端側智能及邊緣側智能的成熟進程，促進AI在企業的部署和客制化，符合集團混合式AI願景。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他又指，集團上季各項業均表現出色，反映集團對正確發展戰略全力以赴、堅定執行、持之以恒的結果，接下來將牢牢抓住AI蓬勃發展的巨大機遇。未來將對創新持續投入，通過富有韌性的全球營運，有信心推動可持續的增長和盈利的提升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14720483-%e8%81%af%e6%83%b3%e6%a5%8a%e5%85%83%e6%85%b6%ef%bc%9adeepseek%e7%82%baai%e5%b9%b3%e6%b0%91%e5%8c%96%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b%e6%9b%b4%e7%8f%be%e5%af%a6%e8%b7%af%e5%be%91-%e7%ac%a6%e5%90%88%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_00992.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-20 15:30:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指收跌不足1點 深指轉漲0.2% 昭衍新藥漲停板",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民幣兌美元匯價回升，滬深A股午後亦曾雙雙反覆轉升；藥股繼續炒上，昭衍新藥(06127)A股(603127.SH)便漲停板。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"昭衍新藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/06127-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"昭衍新藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/06127-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">昭衍新藥官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指經過早市大部份時間報跌的整固後，午市轉為好淡爭持，高位稍微提升至3355點，升4點，低位依然是高市的3338點，全日高低位相差僅17點；滬指收報3350點，跌不足1點或0.02%，成交6700.99億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指則於午後不久開始轉升，並一直維持升市至收市，高位提升至10826點，升53點，與早市造出的全日低位10726點亦只相差不足100點；深指收報10794點，升21點或0.2%，成交1.09萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數仍跌11點或0.29%，以3928點收市；創業板指數亦微跌1點或0.06%，報2225點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泰格醫藥官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250220_FI_source-web_03347.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泰格醫藥官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250220_FI_source-web_03347.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泰格醫藥官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">商務部與發改委發布《2025年穩外資行動方案》，提到要推動生物醫藥領域有序開放，藥股隨之借勢炒上。在中港兩地均有上市的藥股中，以昭衍新藥A股表現最佳，於午後升10%後漲停板；泰格醫藥(03347)A股(300347.SZ)也升8.97%，報59.18元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">康龍化城(03759)A股(300759.SZ)則漲6.06%，報28.51元；凱萊英(06821)A股(002821.SZ)升幅同樣擴大，全日升5.57%，報85.93元；海普瑞(09989)A股(002399.SZ)升3.99%，報11.74元。藥明康德(02359)A股也升2.98%，報64.36元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230704-174914_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230704-174914_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">近期強勢的芯片股回吐，華虹半導體(01347)A股(688347.SH)跌3.4%，報58.23元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)亦跌2.68%，報99.211元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電信股也受壓，中國聯通(00762)A股(600050.SH)跌幅擴大至3.73%，報6.2元；中國電信(00728)A股(601728.SH)跌2.98%，報7.82元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14720461-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b31%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%bd%89%e6%bc%b20-2-%e6%98%ad%e8%a1%8d%e6%96%b0%e8%97%a5%e6%bc%b2%e5%81%9c%e6%9d%bf",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-20 15:15:56",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
